lead_paragraph: LeBron James' rested legs were strong enough in the fourth quarter to carry the Cleveland Cavaliers over the pesky Los Angeles Lakers on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Big Three Return but Cavaliers Given Fright by Lowly Lakers
